articles.author: Alexander Dinger, Lennart Pfahler, Tim Röhn
articles.title: Moldova warns of Russian ‘disruptive’ moves against overseas voting in Sunday’s runoff - POLITICO Europe
articles.description: Moscow’s “disruptive activities” could include fake bomb threats, according to documents obtained by Welt am Sonntag.
